Package: slonana-validator
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libssl3 (>= 3.0.0), libstdc++6 (>= 11.0.0)
Maintainer: Slonana Labs <contact@slonana.dev>
Description: High-performance C++ Solana validator implementation
 Slonana.cpp is a high-performance C++ implementation of a Solana validator
 that provides full compatibility with the Solana network while delivering
 superior performance and reliability.
 .
 Features:
  * Full Solana protocol compatibility
  * High-performance SVM execution engine
  * Comprehensive monitoring and metrics
  * Hardware wallet support
  * Production-ready deployment tooling
 .
 This package includes the validator binary, configuration files, and
 deployment scripts for running a Solana validator node.